<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Event Approval Required</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #f57c00;
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;
    }
    .content {
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      padding: 25px;
      border-left: 1px solid #ddd;
      border-right: 1px solid #ddd;
    }
    .footer {
      background-color: #f1f1f1;
      padding: 15px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: #666;
      border-radius: 0 0 5px 5px;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
    }
    .highlight {
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #f57c00;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #f57c00;
      color: white;
      padding: 12px 25px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .event-details {
      background-color: #fff3e0;
      border-left: 4px solid #f57c00;
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .action-required {
      color: #d32f2f;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Event Approval Required</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Dear <%= name %>,</p>
      
      <p><span class="action-required">ACTION REQUIRED:</span> A new event has been created for <span class="highlight"><%= organizationName %></span> and is awaiting your approval:</p>
      
      <div class="event-details">
        <p><strong>Event Name:</strong> <%= eventName %></p>
        <p><strong>Date:</strong> <%= eventDate %></p>
        <p><strong>Time:</strong> <%= eventStartTime %> - <%= eventFinishTime %></p>
        <p><strong>Duration:</strong> <%= timePeriod %></p>
        <p><strong>Mode:</strong> <%= eventMode %></p>
        <p><strong>Type:</strong> <%= eventType %></p>
        <p><strong>Venue:</strong> <%= eventVenue %></p>
        <p><strong>Event President:</strong> <%= eventPresident %></p>
        <p><strong>Submitted by:</strong> <%= presidentName %> (Organization President)</p>
      </div>
      
      <p>Please review this event request and approve or reject it at your earliest convenience.</p>
      
      <center><a href="<%= eventReviewUrl %>" class="button">Review Event Now</a></center>
      
      <p>If you have any questions about this event, please contact the organization's president directly.</p>
      
      <p>Thank you for your prompt attention to this matter.</p>
      
      <p>Best regards,<br>
      The EventLink Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply directly to this email.</p>
      <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> EventLink. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>